data.description: $5000 in Seller Concessions offered! 5/3 or 4/3 + large office, located in Country Acres subdivision in Lindale, TX! If you are looking for a home with 2 master suites, then this is the one for you and your family! One of the master suites has a separate shower and bath. The other master suite has a shower only. Both masters have large, walk-in closets. Go to the other side of the home to find the 3 remaining bedrooms that share a shower/tub combo. Living room with woodburning fireplace and dining area are open to one another and gives ample space to have fun with the whole family! Walk through the kitchen to get to the backyard. Step onto the covered patio to find a huge backyard where a small bridge takes you to the firepit area, playhouse, and extra fenced in area for pets, if needed. There is a workman's shed and a smaller, walk-in shed for storing your landscaping equipment and outdoor materials. Woods behind the home. Carpet needs to be replaced and is in LR, 1 of the Master Bedrooms, hall, and 3 bedrooms. No garage as it was converted into the 2nd master suite.
